finger-prints with those of CSFv from Poland, other recent European
outbreaks, the previous German outbreaks, and the virus(es) circulating in
the local boars. Apparently they are currently subtyping the virus at the
Federal Institute for Animal Virological Diseases, Riems Island. - Mod.MHJ
